p: The present study also investigated the cytotoxicity of the extracts from the six red propolis samples obtained by conventional extraction and ultrasound-assisted extraction against four tumor cell lines: HCT116 (human colon), HL60 (leukemia), PC3 (prostate carcinoma), and SNB19 (glioblastoma), with the aim of evaluating antiproliferative effects, as shown in Fig 5 (percentage inhibition).
